Package <Unnamed>

Class Summary
HumanOthelloPlayer A HumanOthelloPlayer object represents a human Othello player.
OthelloGame An OthelloGame object represents an Othello game.
OthelloPlayer This is the top-level class for all player classes.
OthelloRunner Application that creates a new Othello game and plays it.
OthelloWorld An OthelloWorld object represents an Othello world.
Piece A Piece object represents a piece in the Othello game.
StupidComputerOthelloPlayer A StupidComputerPlayer object represents a computer player who selects a move by randomly chosing from the allowed locations.
